com.emc.storageos.model.block

Class Copy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.storageos.model.block.Copy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Copy
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Specifies the copy to be operated on type: type of protection (rp, native, srdf) sync: synchronize the mirror copyID: the URI of the copy to be operated on, if none specified operate on all copies for that type name: name of a new mirror being created by start operation. name in the case of a failover operation. count: number of mirrors to create using start operation pointInTime: any point-in-time - used for the failover operation
    See Also:
